data.text:
MORE INFO

Lil Wayne presents his first-ever career-spanning compilation album, I Am Music. The 18 track collection boasts his latest single, Kant Nobody (feat. DMX) produced by Swizz Beatz, Tha Carter IV standout 6 Foot 7 Foot (feat. Cory Gunz) and other hits, including the diamond-certified smash Lollipop (feat. Static Major), Mona Lisa (feat. Kendrick Lamar), Drop The World (feat. Eminem), A Milli, Fire Man, Go DJ and more. Available on translucent ruby double vinyl exclusively for RSD Black Friday 2023.

SIDE A:

1. Kant Nobody  Lil Wayne & DMX

2. Lollipop  Lil Wayne & Static Major

3. A Milli

4. BedRock  Young Money & Lloyd

5. 6 Foot 7 Foot  Lil Wayne & Cory Gunz

SIDE B:

6. How To Love

7. Right Above It  Lil Wayne & Drake

8. Drop The World  Lil Wayne & Eminem

9. She Will  Lil Wayne & Drake

10. Mirror  Lil Wayne & Bruno Mars

SIDE C:

11. Mrs. Officer  Lil Wayne, Bobby V & Kidd Kidd

12. Blunt Blowin'

13. Mona Lisa  Lil Wayne & Kendrick Lamar

14. Uproar  Lil Wayne & Swizz Beatz
